That's a typo. :-/ 
Two lines further in the same mail there was:
bash-2.05a# cat /proc/tty/driver/serial
serinfo:1.0 driver revision:
0: uart:16550A port:000003F8 irq:4 tx:31 rx:7 RTS|CTS|DTR|DSR
        ^^^^^^
So I meant 16550A. Sorry.
